{"article_id":"5Xb3NZy1XBy3TR4G","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Get breaking news alerts and special reports .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"The news and stories","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"that matter ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"delivered weekday mornings .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"Authorities in Georgia ruled Sunday","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that the fatal police shooting of Rayshard Brooks outside an Atlanta Wendy 's was a homicide .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Brooks , 27 , died","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"after he was shot twice in the back on Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"the Fulton County Medical Examiner 's Office said in a statement .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Brooks was shot after a confrontation with two Atlanta police officers in the parking lot .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Police had been summoned there on a report of a man","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"sleeping in his car in the drive-through .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Let our news meet your inbox .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"The news and stories","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that matters ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"delivered weekday mornings .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"This site is protected by recaptcha","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Brooks struggled with the officers","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"after they administered a field sobriety test","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"and tried to take him into custody .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Surveillance video appears to show Brooks running away from the officers with a stun gun","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"that he 'd taken from one of them ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"said Vic Reynolds , director of the Georgia Bureau of Investigation .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"While running ,","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"Brooks appeared to turn around","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"and point the weapon at police ,","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"Reynolds said","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"`` At that point , the Atlanta officer reaches down","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"and retrieves his weapon from his holster ,","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"discharges it ,","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"strikes Mr. Brooks there on the parking lot ,","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"and he goes down . ''","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"L. Chris Stewart , an attorney for Brooks ' family , said","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Brooks should n't have faced deadly force","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"because he appeared to have a stun gun .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"`` Of extreme concern in the murder of Rayshard Brooks is the fact","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that he was shot in the back multiple times","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"while fleeing , ''","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Stewart and law partner Justin Miller said in a statement Saturday .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Atlanta Police Chief Erika Shields resigned over the shooting ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"saying in a statement","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"that `` it is time","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"for the city to move forward","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"and build trust between law enforcement and the communities","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"they serve . ''","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"Garrett Rolfe , the officer","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"who shot Brooks ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"was fired .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"A second officer , Devin Brosnan , was placed on administrative duty .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Neither officer has been charged with a crime .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"The Georgia Bureau of Investigation is reviewing the incident .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"Full coverage of George Floyd 's death and protests around the country","depth":3},{"id":52,"text":"The shooting prompted protests Saturday night near the Wendy 's ,","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"which was set on fire .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"Brooks ' death comes amid widespread protests over the May 25 killing of George Floyd in Minneapolis .","depth":5},{"id":55,"t